      <title>格鲁吉亚分离地区议会投票反对与俄罗斯达成投资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/parliament-breakaway-georgian-region-votes-against-investment-agreement-with-2024-12-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯支持的格鲁吉亚分离地区阿布哈兹的议会周二投票反对批准与莫斯科的投资协议，该协议在上个月引发了抗议，导致该地区自封的总统被罢免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/parliament-breakaway-georgian-region-votes-against-investment-agreement-with-2024-12-03/</guid>
